Sure, here are 25 Midjourney Prompts with a little dog:

1. A cute little dog playing fetch with its favorite toy, wagging its tail with excitement.
2. A curious little dog sniffing around a new environment, exploring its surroundings with interest.
3. A sleepy little dog snuggled up in its bed, dozing off in a peaceful slumber.
4. A brave little dog standing up to a larger animal, barking and showing its teeth to defend its territory.
5. A happy little dog wagging its tail and jumping up to greet its owner with a lick on the face.
6. A clever little dog learning a new trick, using its intelligence and focus to master the task.
7. A playful little dog chasing its own tail, spinning around in circles with glee.
8. A sneaky little dog trying to steal a treat from the counter, using stealth and cunning to avoid getting caught.
9. A loyal little dog following its owner everywhere, eager to be by their side no matter what.
10. A determined little dog pulling its owner along on a walk, showing off its strength and tenacity.
11. An excitable little dog jumping up and down with excitement, unable to contain its enthusiasm.
12. A protective little dog barking at strangers, alerting its owner to potential dangers.
13. A curious little dog watching a bird outside the window, dreaming of the day when it can catch one.
14. A happy little dog playing in the park, running around and making new friends.
15. A friendly little dog greeting other dogs on the street, wagging its tail and sniffing noses.
16. A mischievous little dog stealing a sock from its owner's laundry basket, running around with it in its mouth.
17. A loyal little dog waiting patiently by the door for its owner to come home, eager to greet them with love.
18. A confident little dog strutting down the street, showing off its impressive posture and attitude.
19. A cuddly little dog snuggling up with its owner on the couch, enjoying a cozy evening together.
20. A funny little dog wearing a silly costume, bringing laughter and joy to everyone it meets.
21. A determined little dog practicing its agility skills, jumping over obstacles and running through tunnels.
22. A curious little dog investigating a new toy, using its sharp teeth and playful nature to figure out how it works.
23. A happy little dog wagging its tail and running around in circles, unable to contain its excitement.
24. A mischievous little dog digging in the garden, getting covered in dirt and making a mess.
25. A brave little dog trying new things, whether it be swimming, hiking, or learning a new skill.
